# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .gitignore — Microsoftexpert terraform-* Terraform library modules (canonical, all libraries)
# Modules created by Casey Wood.  Connect with him at https://www.linkedin.com/in/microsoftexpert 
#
# Committed on purpose — do NOT add these below:
#   providers.tf  variables.tf  main.tf  outputs.tf  README.md  SCOPE.md
#   .gitignore  examples/
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Terraform working dir / provider plugin cache (large; never commit) ──
.terraform/
.terraform.tfstate.lock.info
.terraform.d/

# Dependency lock — excluded for LIBRARY modules (providers.tf already pins
# the versions, so it is redundant here). A ROOT module WOULD commit this.
.terraform.lock.hcl

# State files — should never exist in a library module (defensive)
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*

# Plan artifacts and crash logs
*.tfplan
*.tfplan.*
tfplan
plan.out
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Variable files — frequently hold secrets; not shipped with reusable modules.
# (If you ever ship an example tfvars, add: !examples/**/*.tfvars)
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json

# Override and CLI-config files
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

# ── Secrets / credentials — regulated FI (GLBA / NPI); defensive ──
.env
.env.*
*.env
*.pem
*.pfx
*.p12
*.key
id_rsa
id_dsa
secrets.*

# ── Python (ingest / util scripts, uv) ──
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.venv/
venv/

# ── Editors / IDEs ──
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── OS junk ──
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ── Misc ──
*.bak
*.tmp
